mainText:
I would like to offer all the employees at Apple my sincerest condolences.&nbsp;

Steve made me excited to be an Apple user.  I always have been and always will be loyal to the idea of making things simple.&nbsp;

Steve has inspired me to get to where I am today in the wireless industry. 
 Apple products make it possible for me to have my job today.  Without them
 my job would still only be an idea.&nbsp;

Thank you for the gift of dreams Steve.
